 of God keeps him, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read himself"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:12","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:5","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:24","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:10","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the evil one does not touch him. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 17:12","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":12},{"label":"1Pt 1:5","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Jd 1:24","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":24},{"label":"Rv 3:10","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read himself"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:5:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We know that we are of God, and the whole world is under the sway of the evil one. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:5:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And we know that the Son of God has come "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":42,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 1:2","book":"1Jn","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:5","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:8","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and has given us understanding so that we may know the true one. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read the true God"},{"kind":"text","text":" We are in the true one —that is, in his Son, Jesus Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 10:38","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":38,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:21",